It confused me too. Transactions may reach the limit while canal sync job is running (with 200 tables in sync).

Thank you very much for your advice. We need to use "group by" for single-value and "explode" for multi-value , which is not  convenient. 

In this way, multi-value and single-value are unified, and group by is unified for each field.
